lass=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n         href=\"/canada-online-casinos/\"\n         style=\"margin-top:8px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:7px 14px; font-size:0.9rem;\"\n         target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        View Canadian Online Casinos\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Card 3: CA Bonus Guide -->\n    <div class=\"tcs-hub-card\"\n         style=\"border-radius:14px; padding:16px 16px 18px; background:rgba(10,12,38,0.9); border:1px solid #313766;\">\n      <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Bonuses</span>\n      <h3 style=\"margin-top:8px; font-size:1rem;\">\n        Canadian Casino Bonus Guide\n      </h3>\n      <p style=\"margin-top:6px; font-size:0.9rem; opacity:0.9;\">\n        Learn how different deposit methods affect welcome bonuses, reloads and no-deposit offers at\n        casinos accepting Canadian players.\n      </p>\n      <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n         href=\"/canada-casino-bonus/\"\n         style=\"margin-top:8px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:7px 14px; font-size:0.9rem;\"\n         target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        Open Bonus Guide\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Card 4: CA Safety & Legal -->\n    <div class=\"tcs-hub-card\"\n         style=\"border-radius:14px; padding:16px 16px 18px; background:rgba(10,12,38,0.9); border:1px solid #313766;\">\n      <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Safety &amp; Licensing</span>\n      <h3 style=\"margin-top:8px; font-size:1rem;\">\n        Canada Safety &amp; Licensing Guide\n      </h3>\n      <p style=\"margin-top:6px; font-size:0.9rem; opacity:0.9;\">\n        Understand how offshore licensing, provincial rules and casino compliance affect withdrawals,\n        security and overall player protection in Canada.\n      </p>\n      <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n         href=\"/canada-safety-legal-guide/\"\n         style=\"margin-top:8px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:7px 14px; font-size:0.9rem;\"\n         target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        Read Safety &amp; Licensing Guide\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<p></p>";
